      <div class="article-teaser">
        <p>If you drive in London you may need to pay the Congestion Charge, Ultra Low Emission Zone (ULEZ) and/or Low Emission Zone (LEZ) charges. Your number plate (Vehicle Registration Mark) will tell us which charges you need to pay.</p>
        
